on in adults.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038678,0.066842,0.092347,0.10136,0.10241,0.10314,0.10084,0.096993,0.093007,0.090599,0.071079,0.042692],"unified_progress":[0.058515,0.097187,0.071806,0.097448,0.099647,0.098979,0.091387,0.092118,0.086244,0.081016,0.070774,0.05488]},{"section":12,"text":"Lipomas pop into my mind first.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027073,0.054817,0.076147,0.09141,0.1008,0.10688,0.10946,0.10746,0.10647,0.10381,0.075489,0.040188],"unified_progress":[0.038854,0.06984,0.086833,0.097385,0.1,0.10296,0.099168,0.095255,0.09028,0.087903,0.07231,0.059216]},{"section":13,"text":"They're super common and usually show up under the skin.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03245,0.044904,0.058748,0.073709,0.088482,0.10101,0.11119,0.11325,0.11707,0.12018,0.089501,0.049521],"unified_progress":[0.038284,0.060575,0.079579,0.091298,0.097986,0.10821,0.10257,0.10061,0.094993,0.089495,0.074582,0.061813]},{"section":14,"text":"But wait, let me think.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.01588,0.036772,0.056175,0.070899,0.083955,0.10003,0.11362,0.1288,0.13848,0.13085,0.089346,0.035191],"unified_progress":[0.030725,0.059795,0.075179,0.085795,0.09549,0.09615,0.099906,0.10451,0.1029,0.11186,0.083928,0.053761]},{"section":15,"text":"Lipomas are often found in places like the arms or legs, not typically the neck.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042371,0.046014,0.056959,0.069835,0.082452,0.095543,0.10764,0.11458,0.12047,0.12284,0.093539,0.047765],"unified_progress":[0.047861,0.062997,0.076355,0.086121,0.093541,0.10169,0.10022,0.10169,0.098142,0.094637,0.078796,0.057949]},{"section":16,"text":"And they're usually bigger than 0.5 cm too.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038093,0.046846,0.058307,0.070021,0.081315,0.093939,0.10548,0.11519,0.12279,0.12226,0.094332,0.051424]